## 🎨 Design System

### Colors (from design-system.ts)
```typescript
import { statusColors, gradients, cardStyles } from '@/lib/design-system';

// Status colors
<span className={statusColors.active}>نشط</span>

// Gradients
<div className={gradients.primary}>...</div>
```

### Icons (from icons.ts)
```typescript
import { moduleIcons, actionIcons, statusIcons } from '@/lib/icons';

// Use consistent icon sizes
className="h-4 w-4"  // small
className="h-5 w-5"  // medium
className="h-6 w-6"  // large
```

### Shadows
```typescript
// Use soft shadows
className="shadow-soft-sm"  // small
className="shadow-soft-md"  // medium
className="shadow-soft-lg"  // large
```

### Glass Effect
```typescript
className="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20"
```

