## 🔄 Before Any Task

### Checklist:
- [ ] Read relevant rules from `docs/rules/`
- [ ] Check if approved component exists
- [ ] Prepare translation keys for ALL 9 languages
- [ ] Ensure RTL support
- [ ] Plan animations with Framer Motion

### If Creating New Feature:
1. Check `docs/COMPLETE_REFERENCE_GUIDE.md`
2. Use existing patterns from similar features
3. Follow sheet/table conventions
4. Add translations to ALL language files

